WEBVTT

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:14.648
So as I have told you, there’s some people who are materialistic,

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:21.388
some people who are
emotionalistic, and some people who are egoistical.

00:00:22.463 --> 00:00:25.114
Now leave all these things on the
sides, 

00:00:25.545 --> 00:00:30.912
then you come in the centre. Now, you are in the centre. 

00:00:30.912 --> 00:00:37.003
In the centre, people
enjoy just the love of their Mother, like Shri Ganesha does.

00:00:38.901 --> 00:00:42.182
Just think how your Mother
loves you. Finished. Can you?

00:00:43.670 --> 00:00:48.423
It’s a very sweet feeling. And who is your Mother,

00:00:48.423 --> 00:00:53.709
if you really believe in Her, in Sahaja Yoga, these two things should solve the problem.

00:00:54.468 --> 00:00:58.546
No more thinking. Just think how much your Mother loves.

00:00:58.968 --> 00:01:05.533
That means you are jumping
onto My Kundalini, and when you jump onto My Kundalini,

00:01:06.419 --> 00:01:10.106
then there is no thought.

00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:20.258
You cannot think. When you think that, how much your Mother loves you, you are jumping onto My Kundalini.

00:01:21.354 --> 00:01:23.011
And that time, there’s no thought.

00:01:24.255 --> 00:01:27.096
The Mother Earth Herself is sucking you down.

00:01:27.862 --> 00:01:28.881
She’s sucking you down.

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:38.991
That is how
you meditate now. This is how you have to meditate,

00:01:39.708 --> 00:01:46.479
and it’s such a security-giving
thing. It will change your expressions, faces, everything.

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:55.000
And that enamoured expression that you find in these people will be on your faces very soon.

00:02:02.320 --> 00:02:07.668
And complete silence will exist once you come on My Kundalini.

00:02:08.693 --> 00:02:18.496
But not through your mental projection, but through your meditative, spontaneous experience.

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:26.892
It’s very joy-
giving. Just feel the joy of that.

00:02:26.892 --> 00:02:37.715
You are all with Me here, and the joy of that feeling will
really enlarge your hearts, and then you can give it to others.

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:47.625
You don’t have to be
crazy about these things, but just to feel it within yourself.

00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:05.771
So the Primordial Kundalini, which is reflected in you as your Kundalini, 

00:03:06.045 --> 00:03:08.214
also is of the
same nature 

00:03:10.240 --> 00:03:27.040
and it works in the same way. It rises, gives you Self Realization, gives you the powers,

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:32.338
but after all one has to know it is a reflection 

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:41.155
and a reflection to make it truthful, real.

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:48.163
You have to look at reality first,

00:03:51.600 --> 00:03:56.183
how the real one,

00:03:56.900 --> 00:04:03.633
the real Kundalini,
the real Primordial One, how it acts, how it works.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:11.048
If you start thinking about My
Kundalini only, immediately you will become silent, no question.

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:15.848
You cannot think, just
you become silent.

00:04:17.324 --> 00:04:24.256
Just think of any one of My chakras and your chakras will be all right.

00:04:25.105 --> 00:04:29.702
But you have to have that depth. You have to have that much protocol.

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:34.298
You have
to have that much right. Just it will act.

00:04:34.784 --> 00:04:42.244
Don’t have to do anything. Just you have to
think of My chakras. Just think about My Kundalini.

00:04:42.624 --> 00:04:43.853
That’s sufficient.

00:04:44.183 --> 00:04:47.394
But you have to
develop that surrendering situation.

00:04:47.710 --> 00:04:50.340
Even now there are Sahaja Yogis who doubt.

00:04:51.130 --> 00:04:54.567
They have seen the work. They have seen everything, still they doubt

00:04:54.904 --> 00:04:59.608
and they yield to
people who are on the periphery.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:05.192
periphery. And there are Sahaja Yogis who are still sticking on
to many things. They cannot change.

00:05:05.192 --> 00:05:09.414
They haven’t got yet that courage to change
themselves.

00:05:10.390 --> 00:05:13.955
I don’t say that you have to change anything outside,

00:05:14.798 --> 00:05:17.437
outside, but a time comes
you might have to change also,

00:05:18.133 --> 00:05:19.585
so you should be prepared.

00:05:20.428 --> 00:05:25.106
How much we are
courageous, that is to be weighed and to be found out.

00:05:26.835 --> 00:05:35.649
Unless and until you have full
courage, you cannot establish Sahaja Yoga in a quick way.

00:05:37.420 --> 00:05:46.491
When you are using your own Kundalini, you have to know that the Kundalini that is your own has problems.

00:05:48.536 --> 00:05:56.884
She Herself has gone through various ages and stages and She Herself is sometimes
very much hurt,

00:05:56.884 --> 00:06:02.004
very unhappy and very weak and then She cannot rise.

00:06:03.163 --> 00:06:09.883
So if you want that this Kundalini that is your own, that is your own mother 

00:06:10.178 --> 00:06:12.470
has to give you all the nourishment and everything,

00:06:13.250 --> 00:06:18.016
you must learn, first of all, foremost thing,
how to surrender to reality.

00:06:20.231 --> 00:06:25.553
So if you learn how to surrender to the Primordial Kundalini,

00:06:26.481 --> 00:06:34.748
then your Kundalini’s immediately strengthened. It’s like this, supposing you have a stone stone 

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:40.881
and you try to put anything on it,

00:06:41.200 --> 00:06:48.251
it won’t reflect. Then you improve the wood, still nothing will be
reflected.  

00:06:49.052 --> 00:06:55.564
Then you paint it, some reflection will come. Then you have the glass. The glass won’t reflect.

00:06:56.640 --> 00:07:03.163
But if you use some mercury and make it a mirror, it will reflect, but still it may not be the perfect mirror.

00:07:03.901 --> 00:07:08.457
So this is how the kind of reflector you are, 

00:07:08.457 --> 00:07:15.665
on that depends the kind of reflection you get and the kind of personality you develop.

00:07:16.931 --> 00:07:24.416
So there should be no aim as such to be dissolved

00:07:26.960 --> 00:07:32.512
 into the reality, should be the desire within you. 

00:07:33.646 --> 00:07:35.334
Start dissolving into it.

00:07:36.007 --> 00:07:41.614
Then one does not have to talk about
detachment. One does not have to talk about anything,

00:07:42.078 --> 00:07:43.572
about any virtues.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:49.212
They automatically come because now you have become the Divine. Once you become the Divine,

00:07:49.212 --> 00:07:57.366
even your Kundalini becomes absolutely, beautifully, completely reflecting the primordial one.

00:07:58.210 --> 00:08:05.258
to go further, you have to have full determination and understanding that this is a tremendous work

00:08:05.258 --> 00:08:10.107
and a tremendous task and all your powers to be awakened within yourself. 

00:08:10.107 --> 00:08:17.219
You have to be first of all fully equipped with readiness,

00:08:17.219 --> 00:08:21.049
readiness to serve the Divine.

00:08:21.176 --> 00:08:28.053
Unless and until you have that readiness, that “I don’t want anything. I don’t want. I just want to serve the Divine.”

00:08:28.643 --> 00:08:38.683
As long as you are striving for it and asking
for it with full heart, with full sincerity,

00:08:39.186 --> 00:08:46.556
then I’m sure this Kundalini will be strengthened and She’ll cleanse you completely and you’ll one day be Mahayogis.

00:08:50.101 --> 00:08:56.730
The Kundalini has definitely enlightened your Mahalakshmi Principle.

00:08:56.730 --> 00:09:02.322
So you can always make out, “What my chakras are? How are they catching?  Where are they catching?”

00:09:02.638 --> 00:09:10.515
Instead of avoiding that, you just work it out: what’s the problem,  where is the problem?

00:09:11.581 --> 00:09:21.516
Once you work it out then you will be surprised that, as soon as your desire goes inward,

00:09:22.221 --> 00:09:27.386
the Kundalini Itself will rush through, and She will cleanse your chakras.

00:09:28.567 --> 00:09:31.920
As I was telling you, we do not know our powers.

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:40.240
Only one thing you have to do is to
desire. You have to desire that: “Let my vibrations be all right.

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:47.360
Let my chakras be
cleared out. Let me be in the centre, in the balance.” Just you have to desire!

00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:51.824
I mean
it’s such a simple thing to desire. But that also we cannot do.

00:09:52.836 --> 00:10:03.483
Our desires are something else, not what we have to be. Just you have to desire that, “Let me be a clean Sahaja Yogi.

00:10:03.841 --> 00:10:08.748
Let me be a solid Sahaja Yogi.” There are mediocres who can never be.

00:10:09.212 --> 00:10:15.271
I am not talking about them. But so many can be very high up,

00:10:15.271 --> 00:10:17.755
can be very high up in Sahaja Yoga.

00:10:18.391 --> 00:10:24.581
But their desires are not yet being fully manifested. 

00:10:25.403 --> 00:10:29.891
So this is the guiding factor for you, this Mahalakshmi Principle,

00:10:29.891 --> 00:10:41.235
which works out everything that is balancing you, the equilibrium and the wisdom. 

00:10:41.699 --> 00:10:49.024
As the light of Mahalakshmi Principle starts, the wisdom dawns upon you.

00:10:49.382 --> 00:10:56.396
But the greatest of all is the love: love for God, love for truth.

00:10:57.008 --> 00:11:01.971
And you thrive on that love. Just you are there. 

00:11:02.688 --> 00:11:06.544
I mean, I asked him, “Why so many are here?” They said, “For the puja!”

00:11:06.634 --> 00:11:11.800
Why? It’s a sign that you are great Sahaja Yogis,

00:11:11.800 --> 00:11:13.640
that you are here because of puja,

00:11:13.767 --> 00:11:20.251
that you understand the value of puja and that you need the puja, that you enjoy because it is nourishing to you.

00:11:20.778 --> 00:11:26.370
It’s a very good thing, because that shows that
you are very much there,

00:11:27.256 --> 00:11:33.884
you are very much understanding the importance of right
things, and you want to do it at any cost.

00:11:35.264 --> 00:11:40.484
All these desires are significant because they show 

00:11:40.927 --> 00:11:45.584
that you are in the Mahalakshmi
Principle and you want to keep on that one.

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:54.705
I would say, there is a simple one that you can do is just to be on my Kundalini,

00:11:56.033 --> 00:12:01.706
if you can: just try to be in my Kundalini, on my Kundalini. Just put attention. You can,

00:12:01.706 --> 00:12:06.526
all of  you can. Any problem, just put your attention onto my Kundalini,

00:12:06.631 --> 00:12:11.367
and you will be all right, you will just become thoughtless, because there’s no thought.

00:12:14.720 --> 00:12:21.890
This is the best way to do it, is to just solve all problems by putting attention on my Kundalini.

00:12:22.353 --> 00:12:26.980
And, by that your ego will definitely dissolve, because then you will know that,

00:12:26.980 --> 00:12:31.024
“Mother is doing everything. I am doing nothing. So why should I be proud of it?”

00:12:32.690 --> 00:12:40.000
Also the conditionings will dissolve because my Kundalini is absolutely pure,

00:12:42.172 --> 00:12:46.905
it’s not
attached to anyone. It is not even attached to Sahaj Yoga.

00:12:47.227 --> 00:12:52.468
It is not attached to anyone.
The job it has got to do is to nourish everything.

00:12:53.522 --> 00:12:58.336
If it can nourish, well and good. If it
does not nourish, well and good.

00:12:58.863 --> 00:13:00.863
It depends on what do you want.

00:13:01.360 --> 00:13:06.433
You want to be nourished: all right, so the Kundalini
is there, the Mahalakshmi Principle is there,

00:13:06.433 --> 00:13:11.931
it will nourish you. But if you don’t want,
nobody is going to force you in any way.

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:19.495
Nobody is going to jump on you or form
some sort of a formidable oppression: nothing of the kind. 

00:13:22.321 --> 00:13:25.781
It’s just like a River Ganges,
you can say, which is flowing.

00:13:26.403 --> 00:13:27.025
Now if you want you can fill up your pitchers. 

00:13:31.187 --> 00:13:34.096
If you
don’t want, She is not going to enter into your pitchers.

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:38.648
She is not going to come in
your house and get into your pitchers.

00:13:38.994 --> 00:13:46.474
So there has to be a desire to get it, and that is what is called as bhakti.

00:13:47.128 --> 00:13:52.098
Bhakti is the desire, the devotion, to get 

00:13:56.653 --> 00:14:05.458
the joy of bhakti. It’s such a beautiful thing. I wish, I could
do the bhakti to someone, but I can’t do.

00:14:07.229 --> 00:14:12.713
Because I see you, when you are in bhakti,
you just get lost into it. So much you enjoy.

00:14:13.219 --> 00:14:14.906
It’s such an enjoyable thing. 

00:14:14.906 --> 00:14:22.215
Then you don’t think, you just enjoy the bhakti. And that’s what is the most coveted,

00:14:23.479 --> 00:14:32.796
the highest, state where you are just one with the Divine and just swimming in the ocean of joy.

00:14:33.633 --> 00:14:41.067
So this Mahalakshmi Principle is to be 
preserved and has to be always watched and looked into.

00:14:41.637 --> 00:14:46.472
And the blessings of Mahalakshmi are so many that, I tell you, 

00:14:46.472 --> 00:14:50.722
I cannot even tell them in one lecture; I’ll have to give at least ten lectures.

00:14:50.722 --> 00:14:55.716
But you yourself
know what are the blessings of this Mahalakshmi Principle is.

00:14:56.391 --> 00:15:02.266
The greatest is the
complete self-contentedness: it’s absolutely self-contented.

00:15:04.400 --> 00:15:10.738
You don’t want to grab something, you don’t want to run after something,

00:15:11.054 --> 00:15:12.843
you are just
self-contended.

00:15:13.760 --> 00:15:22.039
You don’t want any publicity, you don’t want any comfort, nothing. You are comfortable in your Spirit.

00:15:23.283 --> 00:15:27.551
This is the greatest blessing of this Mahalakshmi Principle.

00:15:29.280 --> 00:15:37.706
And, if that is so, then why not we look after our Mahalakshmi Principle and forget about the rest.

00:15:40.105 --> 00:15:41.755
May God bless you all.
